| publisher=[[Los Angeles Times]]
| author=[[Richard A. Serrano]], [[John Daniszewski]]
| date=May 22, 2005
| accessdate=2007-12-24
}}</ref><ref name=BBC20050519> 
{{cite news
| url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4564405.stm
| title=Red Cross 'raised Koran concerns'
| publisher=[[BBC]]
| date= 19 May 2005
