[[Shehzad Tanweer]], who participated in the [[7 July 2005 London bombing]], may have had his ideology reinforced by allegations of Qur'an abuse. His cousin Mohammad Saleem noted that "Incidents like desecration of the Koran have always been in his mind."<ref name=TheTimes20050722> 
